OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with the odd shower.
OL,7,FStaying cloudy overnight with some
OL,8,Foccasional rain later in the night.
OL,9,FFresh occasionally strong southerly
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA cloudy day with occasional
OL,13,Frain, but some drier spells of weather
OL,14,Ftoo. Strong southwesterly winds at
OL,15,Ffirst.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
